<p>The green revolution is here, and Filipino shoppers are leading the charge! In 2025, eco-friendly and sustainable products are not just trending on Shopee Philippines—they're becoming the new normal. Whether you're looking to reduce plastic waste, support sustainable brands, or simply make more conscious purchasing decisions, Shopee has become the go-to destination for green shopping.</p>

